{"type":"message","id":"26426b47","parentId":"ae8a580f","timestamp":"2026-02-20T02:04:54.829Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:31240d42-43aa-4b12-8a55-cdada12782a9 A股每日资讯] 请抓取最新的A股资讯（人工智能、机器人、热门板块相关），整理成【HTML简报格式】发送到邮箱 qn_home@163.com，标题格式为：A股开盘前资讯 - 今日日期。\n\n【重要要求】\n1. 必须从【至少4个不同来源】抓取资讯：第一财经、东方财富、新浪财经、同花顺、财联社、每日经济新闻等\n2. 【不要放链接】- 将资讯要点直接总结展示在邮件正文中，每条资讯需要包含【标题+100字左右的内容摘要】\n3. 使用 /root/.openclaw/workspace/a-stock-news-v4.html 作为样式模板\n4. 每个板块至少精选【TOP 10条】重要资讯\n5. 确保包含：标题、日期、机器人/AI板块、美股市场、机构观点、科创板、宏观数据等板块\n6. 【邮件发送】：必须以MIME text/html 格式发送邮件，确保邮件显示为渲染后的HTML页面\nCurrent time: Friday, February 20th, 2026 — 10:04 AM (Asia/Shanghai)\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1771553094826}}
{"type":"message","id":"71a8e21e","parentId":"26426b47","timestamp":"2026-02-20T02:05:02.505Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求我抓取最新的A股资讯（人工智能、机器人、热门板块相关），整理成HTML简报格式发送到邮箱 qn_home@163.com。\n\n要求：\n1. 从至少4个不同来源抓取资讯\n2. 不要放链接，将资讯要点直接总结展示，每条资讯需要包含标题+100字左右的内容摘要\n3. 使用 /root/.openclaw/workspace/a-stock-news-v4.html 作为样式模板\n4. 每个板块至少精选TOP 10条重要资讯\n5. 确保包含：标题、日期、机器人/AI板块、美股市场、机构观点、科创板、宏观数据等板块\n6. 邮件发送：必须以MIME text/html格式发送\n\n首先，我需要：\n1. 查看样式模板 /root/.openclaw/workspace/a-stock-news-v4.html\n2. 抓取多个财经网站的A股资讯\n3. 整理成HTML格式\n4. 发送邮件\n\n让我先查看样式模板，然后开始抓取资讯。","thinkingSignature":"4ddb1d8597e4b2cf80bcfe178b13a25df094582e0ca5eefdac9c1818d70a28cf"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_epcgijz28osx_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/a-stock-news-v4.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":28,"output":244,"cacheRead":7823,"cacheWrite":3617,"totalTokens":11712,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771553094828}}
{"type":"message","id":"6d07f2f9","parentId":"71a8e21e","timestamp":"2026-02-20T02:05:02.522Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_epcgijz28osx_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>A股开盘前资讯</title>\n    <style>\n        body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; background: #f5f5f5; margin: 0; padding: 20px; }\n        .container { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; background: #fff; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }\n        .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a73e8, #4285f4); color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; }\n        .header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 28px; }\n        .header p { margin: 10px 0 0; opacity: 0.9; font-size: 14px; }\n        .section { padding: 24px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; }\n        .section:last-child { border-bottom: none; }\n        .section-title { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; color: #1a73e8; margin: 0 0 16px 0; display: flex; align-items: center; }\n        .section-title::before { content: ''; display: inline-block; width: 4px; height: 20px; background: #1a73e8; border-radius: 2px; margin-right: 10px; }\n        .news-item { padding: 12px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0; }\n        .news-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }\n        .news-title { font-size: 15px; color: #333; margin: 0 0 6px 0; line-height: 1.5; }\n        .news-title a { color: #1a73e8; text-decoration: none; }\n        .news-title a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }\n        .news-meta { font-size: 12px; color: #888; }\n        .tag { display: inline-block; padding: 2px 8px; background: #e8f0fe; color: #1a73e8; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 11px; margin-right: 8px; }\n        .tag-hot { background: #ffe0e0; color: #d93025; }\n        .footer { background: #f8f8f8; padding: 20px; text-align: center; color: #666; font-size: 12px; }\n        .source-tag { display: inline-block; padding: 2px 6px; background: #e0e0e0; color: #666; border-radius: 3px; font-size: 10px; margin-right: 8px; }\n        .source-yicai { background: #ff6b6b; color: white; }\n        .source-eastmoney { background: #4ecdc4; color: white; }\n        .source-163 { background: #ff9f43; color: white; }\n        .source-sina { background: #ee5a24; color: white; }\n        .source-10jqka { background: #00d2d3; color: white; }\n        .section-header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }\n        .news-count { font-size: 12px; color: #888; font-weight: normal; }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"header\">\n            <h1>📈 A股开盘前资讯</h1>\n            <p>2026年2月18日 · 星期三</p>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"section\">\n            <div class=\"section-header\">\n                <h2 class=\"section-title\">🤖 机器人板块 <span class=\"news-count\">(TOP 20)</span></h2>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <h3 class=\"news-title\"><a href=\"https://www.yicai.com/news/103053982.html\" target=\"_blank\">宇树机器人马年秀出\"赛博真功夫\"，突破运动性能极限</a></h3>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-yicai\">第一财经</span>2026-02-17</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <h3 class=\"news-title\"><a href=\"https://www.163.com/dy/article/KM2HQP310519875F.html\" target=\"_blank\">魔法原子机器人\"霸屏\"春晚，具身智能资本风向生变</a></h3>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-163\">网易财经</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <h3 class=\"news-title\"><a href=\"https://www.163.com/dy/article/KM2HQP310519875F.html\" target=\"_blank\">这个春节999元租个人形机器人拜年，然后呢？</a></h3>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-163\">网易财经</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <h3 class=\"news-title\"><a href=\"https://www.163.com/dy/article/KM2HQP310519875F.html\" target=\"_blank\">当春晚进入智能科技周期，追觅站上C位</a></h3>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-163\">网易财经</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <h3 class=\"news-title\"><a href=\"https://www.163.com/dy/article/KM2HQP310519875F.html\" target=\"_blank\">不止有机器人！这抹\"中国红\"也是春晚的隐藏主角</a></h3>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-163\">网易财经</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <h3 class=\"news-title\"><a href=\"https://www.yicai.com/news/103053860.html\" target=\"_blank\">中大型无人机首次集群亮相春晚，还有这些低空飞行器登场</a></h3>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-yicai\">第一财经</span>2026-02-17</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <h3 class=\"news-title\"><a href=\"https://www.163.com/dy/article/KM2HQP310519875F.html\" target=\"_blank\">宇树科技王兴兴：今年宇树科技的目标出货量在1-2万台左右</a></h3>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-163\">网易财经</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <h3 class=\"news-title\"><a href=\"https://www.163.com/dy/article/KM2HQP310519875F.html\" target=\"_blank\">亿元\"入场券\"背后的暗战：机器人企业为何砸重金拼春晚？</a></h3>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-163\">网易财经</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <h3 class=\"news-title\"><a href=\"https://www.yicai.com/news/103054260.html\" target=\"_blank\">两个